	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Other than where to mount the Famicom connector, it sounds like it will be a very straight-forward mod.  It should work just fine.
<br />
<br />If you want FC carts to use the sound I/O pins, you'll find their NES counterparts on the bottom expansion port.

		

		</td>
